OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffire services - report     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Evidence of bullying, harassment and   
OL,6, discrimination in every fire and rescue
OL,7, service in England, could be "just the 
OL,8, tip of the iceberg", say inspectors.   
OL,10,FIn about a quarter of the 44 services, 
OL,11,Ftheir report found staff complaints of 
OL,12,Fhomophobic, sexist and racist behaviour
OL,13,F- often excused as banter.             
OL,15,FCases include male firefighters telling
OL,16,Fa colleague they would rape her and a  
OL,17,Fsenior officer using a racial slur.    
OL,19,FThe government called the findings     
OL,20,F"deeply concerning".                   
